Package BobcatLib.Hardware.Controllers

Class EightBitDo

java.lang.Object
BobcatLib.Hardware.Controllers.EightBitDo
All Implemented Interfaces:
ControllerWrapper
public class EightBitDo extends Object implements ControllerWrapper
Wrapper class for the EightBitDo controller using WPILib's CommandJoystick. This class provides mappings for the controller's axes, buttons, and D-Pad.
